{"tid":1725874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩名德國學生在港涉非法集結及違反蒙面法被捕","createTime":"2019-11-16T02:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T03:13:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5c54bed4094560bcde0cfca766903c2cd183e189","tid":1725874,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:10:16.000Z","msg":"警方證實，拘捕兩名外籍男子，涉及非法集結和違反《禁止蒙面規例》。法新社報道說，他們是在港的德國學生。<br />\n<br />\n警方則說，星期四晚上約9時，警員發現一批示威者在屯門鄉事會路與杯渡路交界聚集，展開驅散行動，其後在屯匯街一個巴士站，截停兩名分別22及23歲的外籍男子。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，經調查後，22歲外籍男子涉嫌非法集結及違反《禁止蒙面規例》被捕，另一名23歲外籍男子則涉嫌非法集結被捕。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492520-20191116.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492520-20191116.htm&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BDDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=fe392e25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492520-20191116.htm&h=9f662749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492520-20191116.htm</a>"},{"pid":"21e9e4aeec1f055dc7da3b52e9e5e396f05073be","tid":1725874,"uid":240004,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:14:58.000Z","msg":"德國手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597ae865e4b15acea38a47d325de378e2cf8a7eb","tid":1725874,"uid":37596,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:16:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾歐盟垃圾德國，自己國民都保護唔到，聲都唔聲吓"},{"pid":"62c0c37c933e5bc5789af561fc9875135d00d6bb","tid":1725874,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21e9e4aeec1f055dc7da3b52e9e5e396f05073be","tid":1725874,"uid":240004,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:14:58.000Z","msg":"德國手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:17:09.000Z","msg":"德文點譯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji